description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the Live April match-up between The Ninjas and The Goddesses.
Isis Love is trapped on the Bay Bridge with a major accident in front of her, traffic delayed for hours. Rain DeGrey is in the audience and steps up to don the blue until Isis can make it to the arena.
The Ninja's take full advantage of this last minute roster change and jump all over the blue team. Vendetta is a power of nature and punishes the Goddesses with brutal hold after brutal hold. The Goddesses are destroyed in this first round of action. When will Isis arrive and will she get here in time to make a difference?
title: ROUND ONE
